**Paths:**
- `src/pages/Caculation/` — Should be `Calculation/`
- `src/pages/piplines/` — Should be `pipelines/`
- `src/pages/Employe/` — Should be `Employee/`
- `src/pages/Inquirie/` — Should be `Inquiries/`

