### FE-007 🟢 LOW — `CalculationHub.tsx` Import — Does This Page Have a Route?

**File:** `src/pages/Caculation/CalculationHub.tsx` (11.6KB)

This file exists in the pages directory but has **no corresponding route** defined in `App.tsx`. It may be orphaned/unused code.

**Impact:** Dead code in the bundle.

